 <description>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd">
&lt;html>&lt;head>&lt;meta name="qrichtext" content="1" />&lt;style type="text/css">
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style>&lt;/head>&lt;body style=" font-family:'.SF NS Text'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;">
&lt;p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">&lt;span style=" font-family:'Helvetica'; color:#454545;">This 0.8&amp;quot; 8x8 monochrome LED matrix includes a driver chip for simple control via an I2C interface. The backpack features address-selection jumpers so you can connect up to four matrices on a single I2C bus.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&lt;/body>&lt;/html></description>
